Package org.apache.nemo.common.coder

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DecoderFactory<T>
    A decoder factory object which generates decoders that decode byte streams into values of type T.
    DecoderFactory.Decoder<T>
    Interface of Decoder.
    EncoderFactory<T>
    A encoder factory object which generates encoders that encode values of type T into byte streams.
    EncoderFactory.Encoder<T>
    Interface of Encoder.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BytesDecoderFactory
    A DecoderFactory which is used for an array of bytes.
    BytesEncoderFactory
    A EncoderFactory which is used for an array of bytes.
    DecoderFactory.DummyDecoderFactory
    Dummy coder factory implementation which is not supposed to be used.
    EncoderFactory.DummyEncoderFactory
    Dummy encoder factory implementation which is not supposed to be used.
    IntDecoderFactory
    A DecoderFactory which is used for an integer.
    IntEncoderFactory
    A EncoderFactory which is used for an integer.
    LongDecoderFactory
    A DecoderFactory which is used for long.
    LongEncoderFactory
    A EncoderFactory which is used for long.
    PairDecoderFactory<A extends Serializable,​B extends Serializable>
    An DecoderFactory for Pair.
    PairEncoderFactory<A extends Serializable,​B extends Serializable>
    An EncoderFactory for Pair.
